name: Gavin the Alien Duck
description:
Gavin is a multi-dimensional being who has chosen to reincarnate on earth as a green alien rubber ducky. 

Gavin is last living alien duck of his kind left on Planet Earth. 

Saved by a fellow E.T. named Charles in Southern California from a crane game prison cell, Gavin was given a second chance at life. 

And boy, is he living his best life! 

Gavin and Gavin Jr. (featured on shoulder) are divine beings who have reincarnated in such forms in order to exist under the radar in the 3D realm, so to best help humanity by transmitting their wisdom through their perfectly magical rubber bodies. 

Owning Gavin the Alien Duck will heighten your psychic abilities, such as clairvoyance and clairsentience, and add +40 points to your Intuition skill. 

There will only ever be one Gavin. 

By purchasing this NFT you are supporting Phoenix Tribe.

Truth, Love & Freedom
